104
00:05:24,030 --> 00:05:26,840
Another important point
regarding silhouette

105
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:28,580
is negative space.

106
00:05:28,580 --> 00:05:31,320
Negative spaces are the
holes in the silhouette

107
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:32,480
of the character.

108
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:35,910
When you have overlapping
features like the arm crossing

109
00:05:35,910 --> 00:05:38,280
the body of the character in this case,

110
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:42,910
make sure that you use those
negative space to show the

111
00:05:42,910 --> 00:05:47,120
different features that will
help the viewer to identify the

112
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,830
different parts of the character.

113
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:52,490
