116
00:05:57,170 --> 00:06:00,090
You should also try to avoid tangent

117
00:06:00,090 --> 00:06:02,450
on your character or on your silhouette.

118
00:06:02,450 --> 00:06:05,830
On this specific pose, the leg get tangent

